                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280703-130-off653 t18280703-130-cd654"></join>, 1 watch, value 2l.; 3 seals, value 2l.; 1 key, value 3s.; 1 ring, value 3s., and 1 watch-ribbon, value 1d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280703-130-victim801" type="victimName">
